<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.9.8" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="group__pinctrl__esp32s3" kind="group">
    <compoundname>pinctrl_esp32s3</compoundname>
    <title>Espressif ESP32S3 pin control helpers</title>
    <innerfile refid="esp32s3-pinctrl_8h">esp32s3-pinctrl.h</innerfile>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Macros for pin control configuration of Espressif ESP32S3. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The macros follow a naming convention: <computeroutput>&lt;PERIPHERAL&gt;_&lt;SIGNAL&gt;_GPIO&lt;PIN&gt;</computeroutput>. For example, <computeroutput>I2C0_SCL_GPIO1</computeroutput> corresponds to the <computeroutput>SCL</computeroutput> signal of <computeroutput>I2C0</computeroutput> mapped to <computeroutput>GPIO1</computeroutput>.</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".dts"><codeline><highlight class="normal">#include<sp/>&lt;zephyr/dt-bindings/pinctrl/esp-pinctrl-common.h&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#include<sp/>&lt;zephyr/dt-bindings/pinctrl/esp32s3-pinctrl.h&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">#include<sp/>&lt;zephyr/dt-bindings/pinctrl/esp32s3-gpio-sigmap.h&gt;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">&amp;pinctrl<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>uart0_default:<sp/>uart0_default<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>group1<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>pinmux<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;UART0_TX_GPIO21&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>group2<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>pinmux<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;UART0_RX_GPIO20&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>bias-pull-up;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>};</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
  </compounddef>
